  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这款3D赛车游戏设计一个清晰的架构图。核心是从Main模块启动，然后进入Game主循环。你觉得怎么呈现比较好？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Main",
        "Game"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Main作为入口点，Game作为核心调度器。那Game模块需要向下连接哪些子系统？渲染部分怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "ThreeScene"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Game要驱动ThreeScene负责渲染，这个关系很重要，需要标注'Renderiza'。另外Game还要导入Car和Track资源，都标注'Importa'。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "ThreeScene",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以ThreeScene是渲染核心，Car和Track是游戏资源。那ThreeScene和Car、Track之间需要连线吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ThreeScene",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，ThreeScene要同时引用Car和Track来渲染场景，这是双向关系。还有几个Hook模块——Physics、Controls、Camera都要从Game挂接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ThreeScene",
        "Car",
        "Track",
        "Physics",
        "Controls",
        "Camera"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加ThreeScene到Car和Track的连接。Physics、Controls、Camera三个Hook模块都标注'Hook'从Game引出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Physics",
        "Controls",
        "Camera"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Camera应该和Physics、Controls有点区别，它其实是事务队列的性质，不是单纯的Hook。我们把它标为TransactionQueue类型吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Camera"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
