      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对了，还有扩展性考虑。我们需要预留两个未来模块：Hub和Editor，都从Game用'Futuro'标注引出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hub",
